pped]: (S, O, TA:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the young of the sandgrouse"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlqaTaA", "text_ar": "القَطَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "), or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the pigeon, while not yet firm,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "strong,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "not advanced in age:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) pl., in this and the following senses,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EawaAtiqu", "text_ar": "عَوَاتِقُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (K.) ―         -b3-  And A girl"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that has attained to the commencement of the state of puberty,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and become kept behind the curtain in the tent,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "house, of her family,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and not been separated to a husband:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, K:) said by IAar to be so called because she has passed forth from the state of childhood, and attained to being marriageable; (O;) or because she has passed forth from the state, or condition, of serving her father and mother, and has not yet been possessed by a husband; but AAF says that this is not valid: or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that has attained to the wearing of the garment called"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "diroE", "text_ar": "دِرْع"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and has passed forth from the state of childhood and of being required to help in the service of her family:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "such as is between the stages of puberty and middle age:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K:) or a woman"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "who has passed forth from the state,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "condition, of serving her father and mother, and from being possessed by a husband:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb:) pl. as above, and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Eut~aqN", "text_ar": "عُتَّقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "also; the latter occurring in a trad. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And A"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ziq~", "text_ar": "زِقّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or wine-skin], (T, S, &c.,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of which the wine is good:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T, TA:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of which the odour is pleasant, because of its oldness:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "wide,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Ibn-'Abbád, O, L, K,) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "good:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "wide"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as applied to a [leathern water-bag such as is called]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mazaAdap", "text_ar": "مَزَادَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) ―         -b5-  And A bow ("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qawosN", "text_ar": "قَوْسٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ")"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that has become altered in colour;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EaAtikN", "text_ar": "عَاتِكٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (IF, O:) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EaAtiqapN", "text_ar": "عَاتِقَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, K) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EaAtiqN", "text_ar": "عَاتِقٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K) a bow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that has become old and red;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, K;) as also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EaAtikapN", "text_ar": "عَاتِكَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S, O.)       -A2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlEaAtiqu", "text_ar": "العَاتِقُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "also signifies"}, {"kind": "italic